        "headline": "Developed on the Sunshine Coast",
        "body": "<p>Dr Alison Jamieson's medical practice in Queensland exposed her to some of the most demanding environmental conditions for skin health.</p><p>The Sunshine Coast environment presents several consistent stressors: high annual UV exposure, coastal wind and salt exposure, heat-related dehydration, and environmental oxidative stress.</p><p>The products combine advanced dermatological actives with carefully selected botanicals and marine extracts to support the skin's ability to function optimally under Australian conditions.</p><p>Aliangé therefore reflects decades of treating skin <strong>in the environment it was developed for</strong>.</p>",
        "bg": "muted",
